<s1 id=ToSelectApptListTA>To View an Appointment List
	<idx>appointment lists<\idx>
	<idx>list, of appointments<\idx>

The appointment list displays all your appointments for the day, week, 
month, or year.  

<list order>
<item>Display the view of the calendar 
that you want the appointment list to show.
<item>Choose Appointment List from the View menu.
<p>Appointments are listed chronologically and show date, time, and 
description.
<\list>

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet tight>
<item> <xref ToScheduleApptTA>
<item> <xref ToSelectToDoListTA>
<item> <xref ToPrintApptListTA>
<item> <xref CalendarApptEditorDialog>
<\list>


<s1 id=ToSelectToDoListTA>To View a To Do List
	<idx>To Do lists<\idx>
	<idx>list, of To Do items<\idx>

The To Do List displays all your To Do items for the day, week, month,
or year.

<list order>
<item> Display the view of the calendar
that you want the To Do list to show.
<item> Choose To Do List from the View menu.
<p>To Do items are listed chronologically and show check box, due date, 
and description.
<\list>

