<s1 id=ToDisplayAnotherUsersCalendarTA>To Display Another User's Calendar
	<idx>calendars, displaying other<\idx>
	<idx>displaying other calendars<\idx>

<list order>
<item> Choose Show Other Calendar from the Browse menu.
<item> In the User Name field, type <emph>calendar-name@hostname<\emph> 
for the calendar you want to view.
<item> Click Show.
<p> The calendar you are viewing changes to display the new calendar.
<!--	<idx>error messages, from Show Other Calendar dialog box<\idx> -->

<p> The Show Other Calendar dialog box displays a message with the name 
of the calendar displayed.  If you typed the calendar name incorrectly,
an error message is displayed.
